<div id="v510.4.4"><span class="G1161 s">Howbeit</span><span class="G4183 s"> many</span><span class="G191 s"> of them which heard</span><span class="G3056 s"> the word</span><span class="G4100 s"> believed</span><span class="G2532 s">; and</span><span class="G706 s"> the number</span><span class="G435 s"> of the men</span><span class="G1096 s"> was</span><span class="G5616 s"> about</span><span class="G4002 s"> five</span><span class="G5505 s"> thousand</span>.</div>
