<div id="v510.4.11"><span class="G3778 s">This</span><span class="G2076 s"> is</span><span class="G3037 s"> the stone</span><span class="G3588 s"> which</span><span class="G1848 s"> was set at nought</span><span class="G5259 s"> of</span><span class="G5216 s"> you</span><span class="G3618 s"> builders</span><span class="G3588 s">, which</span><span class="G1096 s"> is become</span><span class="G2776 s"> the head</span><span class="G1519 s"> of</span><span class="G1137 s"> the corner</span>.</div>
