<div id="v510.4.14"><span class="G1161 s">And</span><span class="G991 s"> beholding</span><span class="G444 s"> the man</span><span class="G2323 s"> which was healed</span><span class="G2476 s"> standing</span><span class="G4862 s"> with</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G2192 s">, they could</span><span class="G471 s"> say</span><span class="G3762 s"> nothing</span><span class="G471 s"> against it</span>.</div>
<div id="v510.4.15"><span class="G1161 s">But</span><span class="G2753 s"> when they had commanded</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G565 s"> to go aside</span><span class="G1854 s"> out of</span><span class="G4892 s"> the council</span><span class="G4820 s">, they conferred</span><span class="G4314 s"> among</span><span class="G240 s"> themselves</span>,</div>
<div id="v510.4.16"><span class="G3004 s">Saying</span><span class="G5101 s">, What</span><span class="G4160 s"> shall we do</span><span class="G5125 s"> to these</span><span class="G444 s"> men</span><span class="G1063 s">? for</span><span class="G3754 s"> that</span><span class="G3303 s"> indeed</span><span class="G1110 s"> a notable</span><span class="G4592 s"> miracle</span><span class="G1096 s"> hath been done</span><span class="G1223 s"> by</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G5318 s"> <i>is</i> manifest</span><span class="G3956 s"> to all them</span><span class="G2730 s"> that dwell</span><span class="G2419 s"> in Jerusalem</span><span class="G2532 s">; and</span><span class="G3756 s"> we cannot</span><span class="G720 s"> G1410 deny</span> <i>it</i>.</div>
