<div id="v510.4.21"><span class="G1161 s">So</span><span class="G4324 s"> when they had further threatened them</span><span class="G630 s">, they let</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G630 s"> go</span><span class="G2147 s">, finding</span><span class="G3367 s"> nothing</span><span class="G4459 s"> how</span><span class="G2849 s"> they might punish</span><span class="G846 s"> them</span><span class="G1223 s">, because</span><span class="G2992 s"> of the people</span><span class="G3754 s">: for</span><span class="G3956 s"> all</span><span class="G1392 s"> <i>men</i> glorified</span><span class="G2316 s"> God</span><span class="G1909 s"> for</span><span class="G1096 s"> that which was done</span>.</div>
